'''WinImage''' is a disk imaging [[Application software|application]] for [[Microsoft Windows]] created by Gilles Vollant Software. It has features such as creating and editing [[disk image]]s and it is capable of opening [[VMware]] & [[Microsoft Virtual PC]] hard disk images.
Even though it has been a 32-bit program from its beginnings, it utilized the [[Win32s]] system API, so it could run on Windows 3.x. The latest version of WinImage which runs on Windows 3.x is version 6.1.
